snd_pcm_hw_constraint_ratdens \- apply ratdens constraint to a parameter
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" snd_pcm_hw_constraint_ratdens
.BI "(struct snd_pcm_runtime *runtime "  ","
.BI "unsigned int cond "  ","
.BI "snd_pcm_hw_param_t var "  ","
.BI "const struct snd_pcm_hw_constraint_ratdens *r "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "runtime" 12
PCM runtime instance
.IP "cond" 12
condition bits
.IP "var" 12
hw_params variable to apply the ratdens constraint
